stories.title: Our fondness for narratives is driving us mad
Bitcoin slumps to a three-month low as cryptocurrencies extend losses
Climate change threatens one of world’s biggest fish harvests – Science – AAAS

stories.text:
Most of the web focusses on the psychological side of Bitcoin. If hysteria will drive it to the moon or if fear will drive it into the ground. If it is the new gold, the future of money, the dotcom bubble of our generation or the new tulip mania.

Here on HN, we might have the unique opportunity to discuss the future among technical people who actually understand the concepts behind cryptography and blockchains.

Maybe it would be cool if everybody made a prediction and put down their reasoning behind it? Then in 10 years we can look back on it and see how close or far we were from reality.
stories.title: Ask HN: What will be the price of Bitcoin in 10 years?
